翻译成中文：31.1The Tenant shall comply with all laws relating to:
(a)the Property and occupation and use of the Property by the Tenant;
(b)the use of all Service Media at vthe Property;
(c)any works carried out at the Property; and
(d)all materials kept at or disposed from the Property.

31.1租户应遵守与以下事项相关的所有法律:
(a) 物业以及租户对物业的占用和使用;
(b) 物业上所有公用事业设施的使用;
(c) 在物业上进行的所有工程;
(d) 物业上保存的或处理的所有材料。
